{"id":230909,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-黑龙江访民梁艳被劳教后表示不会放弃上/","date":"2012-06-12T20:59:18Z","modified":"2012-06-12T20:59:18Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江访民梁艳被劳教后表示不会放弃上访（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，黑龙江省七台河市访民梁艳因上访被黑保安自北京抓回七台河市，关押在七台河市看守所，没有任何的法律文书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span><span>小时后，家属找到看守所才得知她的消息，梁艳被关押在看守所一直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>。最后被判劳教一年，监外执行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，梁艳家属去七台河市公安局要梁艳被劳教一年的法律文书，七台河公安局说黑龙江省劳动教养委员会判处劳教梁艳劳教一年，监外执行。但判决书上没有省劳教委员会的印章，只有七台河市劳教委员会印章。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，梁艳表示，七台河市公安局长朱孔勤，是黑龙江十大法治人物，他对梁艳家遭遇十分清楚，深知梁艳是受害者，但是依然在看守所中折磨梁艳，关禁闭，戴脚镣手铐两天两夜，逼梁艳签字。梁艳表示还要接着上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/04/blog-post_51.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/04/blog-post_51.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4M9dxNjGi3I/T9cpGQnoQ0I/AAAAAAAAIaw/-bP-kw1d0Bs/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4M9dxNjGi3I/T9cpGQnoQ0I/AAAAAAAAIaw/-bP-kw1d0Bs/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"250\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-786829236769299402?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/d3a6f0271.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文